Title: Introduction to the Thermodynamics of Spin Chains
Authors: Luca Mezincescu and Rafael I. Nepomechie
Comments: 24 pages (1 figure not included, but available on request) (To appear
  in the Proceedings of the NSERC-CAP Workshop on Quantum Groups, Integrable
  Models and Statistical Systems, Kingston, Canada 13 -17 July 1992)
Report-no: UMTG-170
\\
  We review how to obtain the thermodynamic Bethe Ansatz (TBA) equations for
the antiferromagnetic Heisenberg ring in an external magnetic field. We review
how to solve these equations for low temperature and small field, and calculate
the specific heat and magnetic susceptibility.
